  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Frequently Asked Questions</p>
    <p>This section addresses common queries about our software, company, and services. If your question is not covered, please contact us.</p>
    <p>What is Insight Hunter? Insight Hunter is an AI-powered financial intelligence platform offering tools for cash flow analysis, forecasts, and business formation.</p>
    <p>How does pricing work? Lite is free for basic use. Standard is $49 per month for teams. Full Enterprise offers custom pricing with advanced features.</p>
    <p>Is data secure? Yes, with local-first options in Lite and encrypted cloud storage in higher tiers, complying with industry standards.</p>
    <p>Can I integrate with existing systems? Enterprise editions support API integrations for banks, accounting software, and more.</p>
    <p>For technical specs, visit the tech page. Company info in about. Updates and news in respective sections.</p>
  </section>
